@Comment:	Time is 0:37
@Comment:	MOT and Chi sit very close with Mot's arm around Chi. Chi remembers all the other visits and readings of VHC. EXP gives retelling as an option but Chi reads the words. He tracks along with his finger , and Mot patiently helps by pointing to picture as prompt for what a word is , and by giving phonetic clues. It's very slow going. Given that the reading is so tedious , I was impressed by the extent to which they held on to the story line.
